("7482","282","faq_items_0_title","1. How do I know whether my investment is secure?"),
("7483","282","_faq_items_0_title","field_6198433c0d304"),
("7484","282","faq_items_0_content","The security of the cryptocurrencies under management is one of our primary goals. To protect the large majority of the fund assets from unauthorized access, the cryptocurrencies that together account for up to 80% of the assets under management (AUM) (variances may occur due to value fluctuations) are held in cold storage with two out of three multi-signature. However, although continuous optimization of the security will remain paramount, we cannot be held responsible for the loss or theft of cryptocurrencies of the fund. Unless the loss or theft is caused by the gross negligence or wilful default on our part."),
