("9178","302","intro_video_excerpt","Blockchains are public ledgers where all transactions and changes are grouped in blocks. Together these blocks form a chain, representing the complete history of the ledger. This is where we get the term blockchain from.\r\n\r\nThis short video explains what a blockchain is and what different innovations we can expect utilising this technological breakthrough."),
