("9185","302","_intro_items_0_title","field_61983b1578b22"),
("9186","302","intro_items_0_excerpt","Cryptocurrencies are cryptographic tokens that exist on distributed computer networks. They allow anyone to freely exchange value and information without the need for third parties, facilitating peer to peer exchange without any central points of failure or control. The underlying technology that has made this possible is known as blockchain or distributed ledger technology."),
